  "detailed_description": "There's been a mishap at the Science Convention - Professor Goodboi needs your help! A rogue football has found its way into the Quantum Machine and it's up to you to get it back out. Hurry! Before it affects all the timelines! And bring your best thinking cap! Guide the ball to the exit in each level by placing your tools in its path.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Physics-puzzle gameplay<br></li><li>42 hand-crafted levels<br></li><li>8 Languages supported (English, Welsh, French, Spanish, Chinese (Simplified), Japanese, Korean, Portuguese (BR)<br></li><li>Steam Achievements<br></li><li>Find hidden cats</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><br><strong>1 - Collect your tools from the vending machine</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/934e65554a482c514ce85bdc83058648.poster.avif?t=1707323786\" width=644 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/934e65554a482c514ce85bdc83058648.webm?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/934e65554a482c514ce85bdc83058648.mp4?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2 - Position your tools with the cursor</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/ae96c4bfb04049f0bc04dc110d5626f6.poster.avif?t=1707323786\" width=612 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/ae96c4bfb04049f0bc04dc110d5626f6.webm?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/ae96c4bfb04049f0bc04dc110d5626f6.mp4?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3 - Release the ball!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/7f76575e1f3ae551906fb6d622c045b0.poster.avif?t=1707323786\" width=664 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/7f76575e1f3ae551906fb6d622c045b0.webm?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/7f76575e1f3ae551906fb6d622c045b0.mp4?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "There's been a mishap at the Science Convention - Professor Goodboi needs your help! A rogue football has found its way into the Quantum Machine and it's up to you to get it back out. Hurry! Before it affects all the timelines! And bring your best thinking cap! Guide the ball to the exit in each level by placing your tools in its path.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Physics-puzzle gameplay<br></li><li>42 hand-crafted levels<br></li><li>8 Languages supported (English, Welsh, French, Spanish, Chinese (Simplified), Japanese, Korean, Portuguese (BR)<br></li><li>Steam Achievements<br></li><li>Find hidden cats</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><br><strong>1 - Collect your tools from the vending machine</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/934e65554a482c514ce85bdc83058648.poster.avif?t=1707323786\" width=644 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/934e65554a482c514ce85bdc83058648.webm?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/934e65554a482c514ce85bdc83058648.mp4?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2 - Position your tools with the cursor</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/ae96c4bfb04049f0bc04dc110d5626f6.poster.avif?t=1707323786\" width=612 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/ae96c4bfb04049f0bc04dc110d5626f6.webm?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/ae96c4bfb04049f0bc04dc110d5626f6.mp4?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3 - Release the ball!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/7f76575e1f3ae551906fb6d622c045b0.poster.avif?t=1707323786\" width=664 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/7f76575e1f3ae551906fb6d622c045b0.webm?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394430/extras/7f76575e1f3ae551906fb6d622c045b0.mp4?t=1707323786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
